Your update key (a GitHub read:packages token, supplied by your provider).

SETUP
  1. Paste the key on the last line of this file (replace the placeholder).
  2. Save it in this same folder as:   .ghcr-token      <- note the leading dot

  On Windows, Explorer will not let you type a name starting with a dot. That's fine:
  just save it as  ghcr-token.txt  and the Start launcher renames + hides it for you.

The key is only used to download app updates. It is never sent anywhere else, and your
clinic data does not depend on it — if it expires, the dashboard keeps working and simply
tells you that update checks are paused.

ghp_paste_your_token_here
